  Locus:
    Page: 50
    Verse: 6
Tags:
  - Character
---
If you want success in life, if you want to influence others, if you want to
progress well in the spiritual path and if you wish to have God-realization,
you must possess an unblemished, spotless character. The quintessence of
man is his character.
